                "config_id": "1192785095",
                "config_name": "Salesforce - Account ICP Score",
                "config_description": "This transformation processes account data from Salesforce, Google Drive, and intent data sources to calculate and update account scores based on specific criteria. It first filters out deleted accounts and those created in 2024, then evaluates accounts against target industry sectors, geographic regions, company size, and annual revenue thresholds. Scores are aggregated and stored in temporary tables, which are then used to update the final account scores. The output consists of tables containing updated account scores, which reflect changes in account attributes and intent data.",
